25:45.720 --> 25:48.166
Myself.
If I can't earn a shilling here tonight.

25:48.240 --> 25:49.287
Huh?

25:49.360 --> 25:51.647
They'll make him
the fucking Lord Mayor next.

25:51.720 --> 25:53.529
Mmm, that's the idea, Charlie-Boy.

25:54.080 --> 25:55.411
Fucking hell.

25:55.480 --> 25:59.041
