26:10.680 --> 26:12.728
Your favourites. Your favourites.

26:12.800 --> 26:13.847
Come on, boys.

26:13.920 --> 26:17.402
'Cause I hope my boy Finn
doesn't fall off that fucking horse.

26:17.880 --> 26:18.961
Come on.

