26:20.440 --> 26:21.646
CURLY: Shut up.

26:26.560 --> 26:27.846
ARTHUR: Oh, you found it.

26:28.480 --> 26:29.686
We nearly gave up.

26:38.600 --> 26:41.080
Did he tell you
what my business with him is?

26:46.840 --> 26:48.524
The same shit the Turks used to smoke.

26:50.160 --> 26:51.207
I wonder,

26:51.720 --> 26:54.166
