more than his brothers?

26:55.240 --> 26:56.765
(CHUCKLES)

26:59.520 --> 27:01.249
TOMMY: Go and watch the race, boys.

27:03.320 --> 27:04.810
The Turk's clean.

27:07.360 --> 27:09.124
