- Oh, I see.

28:18.320 --> 28:19.924
I thought you trusted women.

28:20.000 --> 28:21.923
I don't trust Birmingham.

28:22.000 --> 28:23.729
I'll have her picked up.

28:23.800 --> 28:26.167
