- By the police, pal.

28:26.960 --> 28:28.246
This is our city.

28:37.360 --> 28:39.124
(ALL CHEERING)

28:49.520 --> 28:51.522
ARTHUR: Fucking beautiful horse, Tom.

28:53.280 --> 28:54.327
Beautiful.

28:55.360 --> 28:57.124
- He's a natural, that boy.
- Yeah.

28:57.200 --> 28:59.407
Good posture. Rides like Dad.

28:59.480 --> 29:00.527
TOMMY: All right, listen to me.

29:00.600 --> 29:04.525
