29:40.520 --> 29:43.046
- Don't be silly, everyone does.
- So go on, then.

29:43.200 --> 29:46.044
-(SIGHS) Cut the snow.
- We call it Tokyo.

29:46.120 --> 29:48.088
We call it whatever
the customer calls it.

29:48.800 --> 29:52.202
In London,
we were told you are all gangsters.

29:52.760 --> 29:55.809
So that's why you got on the train
to dirty, old Birmingham.

29:57.120 --> 29:58.804
For a dirty, old night.

30:02.200 --> 30:03.770
You don't look like the others.

30:03.840 --> 30:05.171
That's the idea.

30:06.360 --> 30:08.806
I put it all together,
but I don't partake.

30:10.240 --> 30:13.084
You see, I've got a bright future,
you see.

30:15.720 --> 30:16.960
