don't you?

30:30.960 --> 30:33.611
There's a cavalry officer
stationed in Ceylon.

30:33.680 --> 30:36.809
And when his tour of duty ends in March,
we'll be engaged.

30:38.600 --> 30:42.082
So I have a bright future, too.

30:43.080 --> 30:44.491
Mapped out.

30:45.400 --> 30:47.448
