30:57.560 --> 30:58.846
(SNORTS)

31:00.560 --> 31:02.005
<i>(BOTH CHUCKLE)</i>

31:09.440 --> 31:10.885
No. Keep it.

31:12.320 --> 31:13.731
As if I were a whore.

31:18.320 --> 31:20.891
Well, if that's the game
you want to play.

31:35.840 --> 31:38.002
(PEOPLE LAUGHING
AND TALKING INDISTINCTLY)

31:42.800 --> 31:43.926
Polly.

31:44.720 --> 31:45.801
Hello, Grace.

31:47.800 --> 31:50.371
You look absolutely beautiful.

31:52.720 --> 31:54.324
Welcome to the family.

31:56.960 --> 31:58.769
