31:59.760 --> 32:01.000
No upsets tonight.

32:01.080 --> 32:04.448
Your hair, everything, beautiful.

32:06.360 --> 32:07.600
Do you know where he is?

32:08.360 --> 32:11.125
Yes. Yes, I do.

32:13.080 --> 32:16.766
