33:10.920 --> 33:12.365
So, thank you.

33:15.760 --> 33:18.240
Let's not forget
I used to do this for a living.

33:20.560 --> 33:22.369
Oh, I haven't forgotten, sweetheart.

33:24.080 --> 33:26.208
It's only Thomas that's forgotten
what you are.

33:26.280 --> 33:28.328
<i>MAN". Ladies and Gentlemen.</i>

33:29.080 --> 33:32.801
<i>The bride and the groom
will now dance alone.</i>

33:32.880 --> 33:34.609
(ALL CHEERING)

33:39.160 --> 33:41.003
(MUSIC PLAYING)

33:46.640 --> 33:49.450
