34:13.400 --> 34:16.005
you run the tracks and sell cars.

34:20.480 --> 34:21.686
Promise me.

34:22.760 --> 34:23.806
Hmm?

34:24.719 --> 34:26.245
A wedding vow.

34:27.880 --> 34:29.166
I promise.

34:30.320 --> 34:31.924
No guns in the house

34:32.920 --> 34:35.161
-and Charles will never see one.
-(CHUCKLES)

34:36.800 --> 34:38.484
I love you, Thomas Shelby.

34:40.840 --> 34:42.126
You keep us safe.

34:43.040 --> 34:44.371
I love you.

34:45.440 --> 34:48.967
And I promise I will make us safe.

34:53.679 --> 34:56.603
MAN: <i>Ladies and gentlemen,
you may now join.</i>

35:11.760 --> 35:13.000
Gate house, come on.

35:25.480 --> 35:26.561
(ENGINE STOPS)

35:26.640 --> 35:31.362
Tommy, Arthur, Collins.

35:31.920 --> 35:36.130
May I introduce you to the
Grand Duchess Tatiana Petrovna,

35:37.640 --> 35:39.563
from Tbilisi, Georgia.

35:40.840 --> 35:45.323
Grand Duchess, may I introduce you
to the Shelby brothers.

35:45.880 --> 35:47.484
Small Heath, Birmingham.

35:50.440 --> 35:53.205
And, uh, good luck with this one, Tom.

35:58.320 --> 35:59.731
Give me the money.

36:01.280 --> 36:03.487
I was told to give it to Mr Kaledin.

36:04.120 --> 36:07.169
Whoever it is up there,
he gave the wrong name.

36:08.480 --> 36:11.643
We asked him the name
and he gave the wrong one.

36:12.200 --> 36:14.362
- What name did he give?
- No.

36:16.440 --> 36:18.283
I don't trust any of you.

36:19.720 --> 36:21.210
Now you give me the money.

36:22.840 --> 36:26.731
