37:09.800 --> 37:12.121
Good. Finn.

37:17.880 --> 37:19.120
(goueus)

37:32.600 --> 37:34.921
Yeah. We're good.

37:36.280 --> 37:38.487
You can go. Moss... (CLEARS THROAT)

37:38.920 --> 37:39.967
