39:53.560 --> 39:56.484
Vehicles, Tommy. Fucking vehicles.

39:56.560 --> 39:58.449
- Nothing about tanks.

39:59.000 --> 40:02.846
Arthur, you listen to me.
You listen to me, all right?

40:02.920 --> 40:05.287
There are powerful people
in this country

40:05.360 --> 40:06.805
who want to help these mad bastards,

40:06.880 --> 40:10.441
