that we hang for one of our many sins.

40:18.200 --> 40:20.851
Now, we've never earned money
like this. Never.

40:21.720 --> 40:25.281
We'll use it to buy
the wharf at Boston docks.

40:25.360 --> 40:27.044
That's why I've asked for dollars.

40:28.600 --> 40:31.729
And when it's done,
it's business as usual.

40:39.000 --> 40:41.970
Come on, brother. It's my wedding night.

40:48.080 --> 40:48.649
(CHATTERING)

40:48.640 --> 40:49.448
(CHATTERING)

40:49.520 --> 40:51.841
- Where's john?
