It's probably just a car back-firing.

47:10.520 --> 47:12.170
(PANTING)

47:49.600 --> 47:51.728
It wasn't the day I was expecting.

47:53.160 --> 47:54.366
Nor me.

47:58.320 --> 47:59.526
It's over now.

48:01.600 --> 48:03.329
Tomorrow it'll be just us.

48:08.960 --> 48:10.325
(SIGHS)

48:11.520 --> 48:12.646
Come here.

48:25.560 --> 48:27.369
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

48:27.440 --> 48:30.091
CURLY: Go on.
You've had a great night.

49:00.760 --> 49:02.171
The water froze in my car.

49:03.800 --> 49:05.404
Uh, they said I could stay.

49:06.400 --> 49:09.609
I know, this is preposterous.

49:10.360 --> 49:12.522
Plenty of other rooms to stay in.

49:17.160 --> 49:19.401
- Goodnight, Mr Oliver.
- You have my card.

49:20.440 --> 49:22.010
Anytime you're in London,

49:22.760 --> 49:24.762
we could have tea.

49:59.760 --> 50:01.569
ARTHUR: I went looking for you.

50:04.080 --> 50:05.605
I thought you'd be in here.

50:07.000 --> 50:08.126
I knew it.

50:09.400 --> 50:11.482
I wanted to end with a bit of peace.

50:12.120 --> 50:13.281
(WHISPERS) Yeah.

50:14.880 --> 50:16.041
Look what I found.

50:18.080 --> 50:20.731
It's beautiful. Thanks.

50:32.000 --> 50:35.083
Arthur, you mustn't worry about
what happened with the speech.

50:40.400 --> 50:43.688
What was in your heart was beautiful.

50:49.200 --> 50:51.806
God hears all the speeches
that don't get said.

50:55.680 --> 50:59.127
And isn't it nice to still be yourself
at this time of night?

51:04.360 --> 51:07.364
Close your eyes, Arthur,
and spend a minute thinking about that.

51:10.920 --> 51:12.604
(MUSIC PLAYING)

51:32.040 --> 51:33.929
(BABY CRYING)

51:34.000 --> 51:35.525
TOMMY: It's all right.

51:35.600 --> 51:36.806
It's all right.

51:49.760 --> 51:50.807
(SHUSHING)

53:05.440 --> 53:06.566
(INAUDIBLE)

53:52.560 --> 53:54.449
(INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS)

54:35.760 --> 54:39.924
More money than all those
fucking toffs put together, eh?

54:41.280 --> 54:44.329
And you're willing to gamble it all
on one robbery.

54:46.080 --> 54:47.730
I'm a gambling man, Pol.

54:48.800 --> 54:50.802
(THEME SONG PLAYING)

55:05.920 --> 55:11.484
<i># Take a little walk to the edge of town
and go across the track #</i>
